\fs22\lang1033\langfe1033\loch\af31506\hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af44\afs36 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f44\fs36\insrsid2508658 \hich\af44\dbch\af31505\loch\f44 Transport Analysis - Requirements Gathering}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\insrsid2508658 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af37\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f37\fs28\insrsid2508658 \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 1) Stakeholder Analysis}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\insrsid2508658 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \li360\ri0\sa120\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin360\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\insrsid2508658 \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 
- Operations Manager: Needs fleet visibility, route efficiency, and on-time performance tracking.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - Dispatcher: Needs trip assignment, schedule control, and quick reassignment workflow.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - Driver: Needs clear trip instructions and simple status updates.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - B\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 usiness Analyst: Needs KPI trends, period comparisons, and exportable reports.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - Executive/Owner: Needs utilization, cost, and service quality summaries.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\insrsid2508658 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af37\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f37\fs28\insrsid2508658 \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 2) User Stories & Use Cases}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\insrsid2508658 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \li360\ri0\sa120\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin360\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\insrsid2508658 \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - As a dispatcher, I want to assign a vehicle and driver to each trip so 
\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 that operations stay on schedule.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - As a driver, I want to update trip status in real time so that dispatch can monitor progress.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - As an operations manager, I want delay alerts so that I can intervene before SLA breaches.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - As an analyst, I want route and\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37  period comparisons so that I can identify optimization opportunities.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 Core Use Cases:
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - Plan and assign trips.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - Execute and monitor trip lifecycle.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - Manage disruptions and delays.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 - Analyze KPI and route performance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\insrsid739448 
